# 1пЄПвГ£ Operators in Java

## рЯФє Types of Operators

### 1. Arithmetic Operators

```java
int a = 10, b = 5;

System.out.println(a + b); // 15
System.out.println(a - b); // 5
System.out.println(a * b); // 50
System.out.println(a / b); // 2
System.out.println(a % b); // 0
```

---

### 2. Relational Operators (Comparison)

```java
System.out.println(a > b);  // true
System.out.println(a < b);  // false
System.out.println(a == b); // false
System.out.println(a != b); // true
```

---

### 3. Logical Operators

```java
boolean x = true, y = false;

System.out.println(x && y); // false
System.out.println(x || y); // true
System.out.println(!x);     // false
```

---

### 4. Increment / Decrement (INTERVIEW FAVORITE)

```java
int a = 5;

System.out.println(a++); // 5 (post)
System.out.println(++a); // 7 (pre)
```

рЯСЙ Trick:

* `a++` вЖТ use then increment
* `++a` вЖТ increment then use

