# 2пЄПвГ£ Control Flow (Decision Making)

---

## рЯФє if-else

```java
int age = 18;

if (age >= 18) {
    System.out.println("Eligible");
} else {
    System.out.println("Not Eligible");
}
```

---

## рЯФє else-if ladder

```java
int marks = 75;

if (marks >= 90) {
    System.out.println("A");
} else if (marks >= 70) {
    System.out.println("B");
} else {
    System.out.println("C");
}
```

---

## рЯФє switch (IMPORTANT)

```java
int day = 2;

switch(day) {
    case 1: System.out.println("Monday"); break;
    case 2: System.out.println("Tuesday"); break;
    default: System.out.println("Invalid");
}
```

---

# 3пЄПвГ£ Loops (VERY IMPORTANT рЯФ•)

---

## рЯФє for loop

```java
for (int i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {
    System.out.println(i);
}
```

---

## рЯФє while loop

```java
int i = 1;

while (i <= 5) {
    System.out.println(i);
    i++;
}
```

---

## рЯФє do-while

```java
int i = 1;

do {
    System.out.println(i);
    i++;
} while (i <= 5);
```

